<p>Every week, your invoice will have delicious recipes to give you some creative ideas for preparing your fruits and vegetables.</p>

<h4>Membership fees</h4>
<p>Membership fees for Localmotive Food Co-operative are $25 per family per year. This fee includes two rubbermaid bins. Each year we charge all co-op members the $25 fee.</p>  

<h4>Bin reeplacement/cleaning fees</h4>
<p>Bins that are returned with excessive dirtiness, smell or wear will be charged a bin replacement or cleaning fee of $7 per bin. We also keep track of the number of bins you have received, and will add a $7 per bin charge for unreturned bins.</p>

